coreframe.data
Class XmlDataSet

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      java.util.HashMap
          coreframe.data.DataSet
              coreframe.data.XmlDataSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map
public class XmlDataSet
extends DataSet

XmlDataSet - XML 문서를 xpath 기반으로 처리하기 위한 DataSet 확장 class 

 XmlDataSet ds = new XmlDataSet("http://www.java.com/xml/test.xml");
 ds.get("/rss/title");  //read
 ds.add("/rss/sender", "writer"); // create
 ds.put("/rss/sender", "writer2"); // update
 ds.remove("/rss/sender"); // delete
  *

Version:
0.1
Author:
manpower http://www-128.ibm.com/developerworks/xml/library/x-javaxpathapi.html
